constitutional amendment for voluntary school prayer which he said 
dannemeyer will soon offer 
the bill makes some changes in the way the money would be 
administered for example it eliminates most of the specific 
categories known as setasides 
a compromise hold harmless amendment addressed concerns 
expressed by some members that no school district be drastically 
cut or get an unexpected windfall in the new funding formula 
that formula provides an increase from the current 32 percent to 
80 percent of federal money is passed through from the state level 
to local school districts community colleges and area schools 
the amendment offered by rep william goodling rpa would 
phase in the new formula over three years with no school district 
being allocated less than 80 percent of what it received in the 
preceding fiscal year 
