fiftysix repairs to about 300 boeing 737s with 75000 or more 
cycles or 60000 flight hours 
thirtyone repairs to about 200 boeing 747s with at least 
20000 flight cycles or 60000 hours in flight 
the proposals are expected to be filed in the federal register 
next week and interested parties will have time to comment before 
